      "id": "51861a2008464760",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "text": "You want to <i>[[ADAPT TO PARTICIPANTS BACKGROUND]]</i>, but you are not completely sure about how to do this regarding the contents the schedule or the methodology. Sometimes it is impossible to make these decisions in advance because the exact skills or interests of the participants are not known.\n  ",
      "id": "82e53daa7fae0c83",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "text": "&lt;center&gt;❖ ❖ ❖&lt;/center&gt;",
